  <span id="freeText8454776516757082485" style="display:none">There was one quote that made this one on my favorites shelf, because lo and behold I look up and see this on the news after reading it.<br> <br><a href="http://s1255.photobucket.com/user/wickedshizuku/media/wickedshizuku001/bush-shoe-throw-033_zpsbc774e13.gif.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
